  "title": "A star-like UFO spotted hovering in Curitiba [1999]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/18/a-star-like-ufo-spotted-hovering-in-curitiba-1999/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-v3",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>FEB 4th, 1999</strong>. Time: 8:00 pm. Duration: 2 minutes. Three people observed an unidentified flying object in the form of a white star in the city of Curitiba, State of Paraná. According to the witness who provided information to COMDABRA [Brazilian Aerospace Defense Command], the UFO remained stationary during most of the sighting and, thus, observed from a distance, it looked like a &#8220;common star&#8221; in the sky, positioned close to the horizon .</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.536. “</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Questionário sobre a ocorrência de objeto voador não identificado na região de Curitiba, Paraná”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n",
  "excerpt": "<p>FEB 4th, 1999. Time: 8:00 pm. Duration: 2 minutes. Three people observed an unidentified flying object in the form of a white star in the city of Curitiba, State of Paraná. According to the witness who provided information to COMDABRA [Brazilian Aerospace Defense Command], the UFO remained stationary during most of the sighting and, thus, [&hellip;]</p>\n",
